WEBVTT

00:13.709 --> 00:16.538
[car door closes]

00:24.198 --> 00:26.287
HEY.

00:29.159 --> 00:30.291
ARE YOU MR. BLACK?

00:30.291 --> 00:33.163
YEAH.

00:33.163 --> 00:34.860
YOU SCARED ME.

00:34.860 --> 00:37.646
[chuckles] YEAH.

00:37.646 --> 00:40.344
SO...

00:40.344 --> 00:42.303
I JUST...

00:42.303 --> 00:45.262
TELL ME WHY I'M HERE.

00:45.262 --> 00:49.136
I HAVE SOMETHING I NEED DONE.

00:49.136 --> 00:52.487
SO DO MOST WOMEN. YOU'RE GONNA
HAVE TO BE MORE SPECIFIC.

00:52.487 --> 00:55.751
RIGHT. YES. SORRY.

00:55.751 --> 00:58.754
UM, WHAT I NEED...

00:58.754 --> 01:01.061
I DON'T KNOW
QUITE HOW TO PUT IT.

01:01.061 --> 01:03.585
WELL, YOU'RE JUST GONNA
HAVE TO OPEN YOUR MOUTH

01:03.585 --> 01:07.458
AND SAY IT OUT LOUD
IN FULL DETAIL,

01:07.458 --> 01:09.678
LIKE YOU'RE TALKING
TO YOUR PRIEST.

01:12.115 --> 01:14.161
YOU SHOW ME YOURS.
I'LL SHOW YOU MINE.

01:14.161 --> 01:16.511
THAT'S HOW IT WORKS.

01:16.511 --> 01:18.513
OKAY.

01:18.513 --> 01:20.515
HERE.

01:20.515 --> 01:23.648
I WANT YOU TO KILL HIM.

01:23.648 --> 01:40.883
HOW MUCH DO YOU CHARGE?

01:40.883 --> 01:42.798
[police radio chatter]

01:45.192 --> 01:47.585
WE THINK SHE WAS KILLED
ABOUT AN HOUR AGO.

01:47.585 --> 01:49.935
NEIGHBOR HEARD SCREAMING,
CALLED 9-1-1.

01:49.935 --> 01:53.374
ANYBODY SEE ANYTHING?WE'VE GOT SAC P.D. CANVASSING,
BUT SO FAR NOTHING--

01:53.374 --> 01:55.376
JUST AN AVERAGE NIGHT.

01:55.376 --> 01:56.986
AVERAGE NIGHT,
AVERAGE NEIGHBORHOOD,

01:56.986 --> 01:58.335
AVERAGE MURDER.

01:58.335 --> 02:00.294
WHY ARE WE HERE?

02:00.294 --> 02:03.601
BECAUSE THE VICTIM IS ASSISTANT
DISTRICT ATTORNEY KELLY FLOWER.

02:03.601 --> 02:05.951
YOU WORKED WITH HER.YEAH, WE ALL DID.
KELLY WAS GOOD PEOPLE.

02:05.951 --> 02:09.085
FORENSICS FOUND A CASING.
SAID IT WAS 9-MIL.

02:12.306 --> 02:15.439
ALMOST POINT-BLANK,
JUDGING FROM THE STIPPLING.

02:15.439 --> 02:17.833
DEPUTY CORONER
SAID NO SEXUAL ASSAULT,

02:17.833 --> 02:21.271
BUT HER NIGHTGOWN'S
RIPPED AND TANGLED.SHE WAS CRAWLING IN IT.

02:21.271 --> 02:23.926
REMODEL?

02:23.926 --> 02:26.972
KELLY'S ONE OF US. HIGHTOWER'S
ALREADY APPROVED THE OVERTIME.

02:26.972 --> 02:30.933
YOU KNOW THE DRILL.WHY IS THAT THE DRILL?
I MEAN, FOR EVERYONE ELSE,

02:30.933 --> 02:33.414
IT JUST LOOKS LIKE FOR YOUR OWN,
YOU TRY HARDER.

02:33.414 --> 02:35.938
WE DO.IT'S A DETERRENT.

02:35.938 --> 02:38.897
IT SENDS OUT A MESSAGE--NOBODY
GETS AWAY WITH KILLING A COP,

02:38.897 --> 02:42.640
A JUDGE OR A D.A.CHO CAN GET A LIST
OF KELLY'S CASES,

02:42.640 --> 02:47.036
SEE WHO SHE PUT AWAY
THAT HELD A GRUDGE.IT'S NOT A DETERRENT.
IT'S REVENGE, REALLY.

02:47.036 --> 02:49.517
I MEAN,
AND THAT'S NOT A CRITICISM,

02:49.517 --> 02:51.388
'CAUSE I'M ALL ABOUT REVENGE.

02:51.388 --> 02:53.999
I MEAN, REVENGE CAN BE
VERY PRODUCTIVE.PRODUCTIVE?

02:53.999 --> 02:56.263
WELL, TAKE RIGSBY.
VAN PELT BREAKS UP WITH HIM.

02:56.263 --> 02:59.570
NOW HE'S IN THE BEST SHAPE
OF HIS LIFE.

02:59.570 --> 03:02.617
I MEAN, HE'S HITTING THE GYM,
WHAT, SIX TIMES A WEEK?

03:02.617 --> 03:05.402
LOOK AT HIM. HE IS BRIMMING
WITH SEXUAL CONFIDENCE.JANE, CUT IT OUT.

03:05.402 --> 03:08.144
[Van Pelt] NOT ON MY ACCOUNT.
IT'S FINE.

03:08.144 --> 03:11.539
SEE? FINE. MY POINT--THERE IS
NOTHING WRONG WITH REVENGE.

03:11.539 --> 03:15.064
VAN PELT, ANY DAMAGE TO
THE WINDOWS OR THE BACK DOOR?

03:15.064 --> 03:18.459
NO, NOTHING.NO SIGN OF FORCED ENTRY,
SO EITHER SHE LET HIM IN, OR...

03:18.459 --> 03:21.113
[Rigsby] HUSBAND'S HERE.HE LET HIMSELF IN.

03:21.113 --> 03:23.638
OH, MY GOD! NO!

03:23.638 --> 03:25.030
KELLY, NO!

03:25.030 --> 03:28.120
NO! [crying]

03:28.120 --> 03:32.995
NO! GOD, NO!

03:39.915 --> 03:43.135
TIFFANY WANTS YOU
TO CALL HER BACK.OH, THANKS.

03:43.135 --> 03:45.529
SAID TO TELL YOU
YOU'RE A VERY BAD BOY.

03:45.529 --> 03:47.749
DID SHE?

03:47.749 --> 03:50.012
AGENT HIGHTOWER, HI.MORNING.

03:50.012 --> 03:53.189
YOU TWO KNOW MARC ODENTHAL
FROM THE D.A.'s OFFICE?SURE. HEY.

03:53.189 --> 03:56.627
[Cho] HI.WE'RE GONNA TALK
WITH THE DISTRICT ATTORNEY.

03:56.627 --> 04:00.152
WHAT CAN YOU TELL ME
ABOUT KELLY'S CASE?WE'RE LOOKING AT ANYBODY
WHO HAD ACCESS TO THE HOUSE

04:00.152 --> 04:03.112
FROM WORK, THE NEIGHBORHOOD,
THE LOCAL DOG PARK, ANYWHERE.HUSBAND?

04:03.112 --> 04:05.767
FLOWER WAS TOO UPSET
TO TALK LAST NIGHT.

04:05.767 --> 04:09.466
JANE AND I ARE HEADING
OVER THERE NOW.AND WE'VE GOT A LIST
OF PAST DEFENDANTS.

04:09.466 --> 04:13.905
AT LEAST FOUR HAVE EXPRESSED
WRITTEN OR VERBAL THREATS.THE D.A. TOLD ME
TO GIVE YOU THIS.

04:13.905 --> 04:16.690
IT INCLUDES HER CURRENT CASES.HANG ON. HANK DRABER.
THE SMUGGLER?

04:16.690 --> 04:18.867
SMUGGLING DRUGS,
CONSPIRACY TO MURDER.

04:18.867 --> 04:21.565
WE HAVEN'T BEEN ABLE
TO LAY A GLOVE ON 'EM BEFORE.

04:21.565 --> 04:24.742
DRABER'S TRIAL WAS SUPPOSED
TO START NEXT WEEK.

04:24.742 --> 04:27.049
I JUST GOT JUDGE HILDRED
TO GRANT A CONTINUANCE.

04:27.049 --> 04:31.140
IT'S GONNA TAKE ME THREE MONTHS
JUST TO LEARN THE FILE.GO. TAKE VAN PELT.

04:31.140 --> 04:33.055
[Cho] ALL RIGHT.

04:39.627 --> 04:42.456
[ship horn blowing]

04:53.293 --> 04:55.033
THERE HE IS.

04:55.033 --> 04:57.558
MR. DRABER!

05:08.743 --> 05:10.962
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

05:14.183 --> 05:16.925
SO HOW ARE YOU GETTING
ALONG LATELY? ANY PROBLEMS?

05:18.927 --> 05:22.060
YOU...

05:22.060 --> 05:26.282
MY WIFE IS DEAD, AND YOU'RE
WASTING YOUR TIME ON ME?

05:26.282 --> 05:28.763
MR. FLOWER,

05:28.763 --> 05:30.721
I KNEW YOUR WIFE.

05:30.721 --> 05:33.942
NOW WE'RE GONNA FIND OUT
WHO DID THIS, EVEN IF IT'S YOU.

05:33.942 --> 05:37.119
YOU UNDERSTAND?

05:37.119 --> 05:39.556
SO HOW WERE YOU TWO
GETTING ALONG?

05:39.556 --> 05:41.515
[voice breaking]
WE LOVED EACH OTHER.

05:41.515 --> 05:43.778
EVERYTHING WAS GOOD.

05:43.778 --> 05:47.085
HOW WAS THE REMODEL?
THAT CAN BE STRESSFUL.

05:47.085 --> 05:49.131
THINGS WERE GOOD.

05:49.131 --> 05:52.221
BUT THAT DAY, WE FOUGHT.

05:52.221 --> 05:54.876
THAT'S WHY I WENT
TO THE MOVIES--

05:54.876 --> 05:56.747
OVER HER HOURS. IT...

05:56.747 --> 06:00.055
[exhales]
IT WAS JUST SO STUPID.

06:00.055 --> 06:03.058
SHE WAS SO STRESSED OVER
THAT DRABER CASE, YOU KNOW?

06:03.058 --> 06:05.408
SHE CALLED IT
HER "CAREER-MAKER."

06:05.408 --> 06:07.932
THAT'S WHAT SHE SAID--
"CAREER-MAKER."

06:07.932 --> 06:10.152
SO YOU ARGUED.
DID IT TURN PHYSICAL?

06:10.152 --> 06:13.460
NO. I LOVED HER.

06:13.460 --> 06:17.115
I WOULD NEVER DO ANYTHING
LIKE THAT. NEVER.[door creaks open]

06:17.115 --> 06:19.988
MR. FLOWER?

06:19.988 --> 06:22.207
I GOT THE TARP ON THE ROOF

06:22.207 --> 06:25.297
IN CASE IT RAINS
BEFORE YOU WANT ME BACK.

06:25.297 --> 06:28.823
DIDN'T MEAN TO INTERRUPT.
I'LL GET OUT OF YOUR HAIR NOW.

06:28.823 --> 06:31.391
THANK YOU. THAT'S
OUR CONTRACTOR CALE SYLVAN.

06:31.391 --> 06:33.088
HE'S, UH--PATRICK JANE.

06:33.088 --> 06:36.831
HOW YOU DOING?GOOD. YOU'RE STANDING
IN THE...

06:40.922 --> 06:44.229
CAN I ASK YOU A QUESTION?
UH, WOULD YOU RECOMMEND

06:44.229 --> 06:46.449
A FLASH HOT WATER HEATER
OVER A REGULAR ONE?

06:46.449 --> 06:49.409
I MEAN, I WAS LEANING
TOWARDS FLASH,

06:49.409 --> 06:53.325
BUT THEY'RE VERY EXPENSIVE.WELL, YOU KNOW, FLASH WILL PAY
FOR ITSELF IN ENERGY SAVINGS

06:53.325 --> 06:57.504
PRETTY QUICK,
BUT IT DEPENDS ON CONSUMPTION.OF COURSE.
THAT'S A VERY GOOD POINT.

06:57.504 --> 06:59.897
UM, DO YOU HAVE A CARD?SURE.

06:59.897 --> 07:01.899
GREAT.

07:01.899 --> 07:04.772
I'LL MAYBE GIVE YOU A CALL.GREAT.

07:04.772 --> 07:07.862
WELL, THANKS FOR
YOUR TIME, MR. FLOWER.

07:11.126 --> 07:13.128
THANK YOU.

07:13.128 --> 07:15.130
CALE SYLVAN IS
A DANGEROUS PSYCHOPATH,

07:15.130 --> 07:18.263
AND HE KILLED KELLY FLOWER.OH? HOW'S THAT?

07:18.263 --> 07:20.614
HE HAD ACCESS,
AND HE LOOKED EVIL.AND...

07:20.614 --> 07:23.094
WHEN I TOLD HIM HE WAS
STANDING IN HER BLOOD,

07:23.094 --> 07:25.706
WHAT WAS HIS REACTION?
NOT HORROR. NOT EMBARRASSMENT.

07:25.706 --> 07:28.012
NO EMOTION AT ALL.
ALL RIGHT. I'LL RUN HIM.

07:28.012 --> 07:30.493
EXCELLENT. HAVING PRINTS
MIGHT HELP, NO?

07:30.493 --> 07:33.235
YOU KNOW, YOU GUYS
SHOULD BE MORE CAREFUL.

07:33.235 --> 07:35.237
YOU ALMOST GOT YOURSELVES SHOT.

07:35.237 --> 07:37.239
IT'S A GOOD THING
YOU LOOK LIKE COPS.

07:37.239 --> 07:39.720
WE COULD TAKE YOU IN,
BUT YOU'LL LAWYER UP,

07:39.720 --> 07:42.287
AND WE'LL ALL WASTE
A LOT OF TIME.

07:42.287 --> 07:45.116
BUT HERE WE CAN HAVE
A NICE CONVERSATION, RIGHT?YEAH. THAT SOUNDS REASONABLE.

07:45.116 --> 07:47.858
FINE. KELLY FLOWER WAS ALL SET
TO FRY YOUR ASS IN COURT.

07:47.858 --> 07:50.992
YOU WERE LOOKING
AT 20 YEARS, EASY.

07:50.992 --> 07:53.429
NOW THE TRIAL'S BEEN POSTPONED
WHO KNOWS HOW LONG.

07:53.429 --> 07:56.867
THAT GIVES YOU MOTIVE
FOR HER MURDER.OH! THAT ONE'S A WINNER.

07:56.867 --> 07:59.130
I KNOW IT IS. [grunts]

07:59.130 --> 08:01.176
HERE YOU GO.
YOU LIKE THE LOTTO, HUH?

08:01.176 --> 08:04.092
NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS. MOM.COME ON.

08:04.092 --> 08:07.051
YOU HAVE PRETTY HAIR.

08:07.051 --> 08:10.185
MY MOM'S A LITTLE SENILE.NOW WHO'D TAKE CARE
OF YOUR MOTHER

08:10.185 --> 08:12.187
IF KELLY FLOWER
PUT YOU IN JAIL?

08:12.187 --> 08:15.103
YOU KNOW, KILLING A PROSECUTOR
IS--IS ALMOST AS BAD

08:15.103 --> 08:17.192
AS KILLING A COP, RIGHT?

08:17.192 --> 08:20.674
IT'S NOT SOMETHING I WANT TO
GET MY HANDS DIRTY WITH.

08:20.674 --> 08:24.416
I GOT ENOUGH PROBLEMS
AS IT IS. RIGHT, MOM?CLOSE YOUR MOUTH, MUFFIN.

08:30.074 --> 08:32.554
WELL, JANE'S RIGHT.
SYLVAN IS A KILLER.

08:32.554 --> 08:34.948
OH! YOU KNOW,
IT FEELS GOOD TO BE RIGHT.

08:37.168 --> 08:41.172
PRINTS BROUGHT UP THESE I.D.s.
WE GOT CARL SENNETT,

08:41.172 --> 08:43.174
A WITNESS IN AN ACCIDENTAL
DROWNING IN ARIZONA,

08:43.174 --> 08:45.655
CORY SAMPSON,
WHO LIVED NEXT DOOR

08:45.655 --> 08:47.962
TO A HIT-AND-RUN VICTIM
IN SEATTLE,

08:47.962 --> 08:50.007
AND CHAD SEWELL,
WANTED FOR QUESTIONING

08:50.007 --> 08:53.141
ABOUT THE MURDER OF HIS BOSS,
A BANK EXECUTIVE IN RENO.

08:53.141 --> 08:56.274
WE HAVE FOUR OTHER DEATHS
THAT SYLVAN'S LINKED TO

08:56.274 --> 08:58.886
IN SOME OTHER WAY.HE'S NOT JUST A KILLER.
HE'S A SERIAL KILLER.

08:58.886 --> 09:01.889
WELL, SADDLE UP.
LOCK AND LOAD. DO WHAT YOU DO.

09:01.889 --> 09:04.021
GO--GO BRING HIM IN.WE CAN'T.

09:04.021 --> 09:05.849
NOPE.WHAT?

09:05.849 --> 09:08.243
ALL WE HAVE IS THAT CALE SYLVAN
LIKED TO CHANGE HIS NAME--

09:08.243 --> 09:11.333
NOT ILLEGAL--AND THAT
BAD LUCK FOLLOWED HIM.

09:11.333 --> 09:16.120
WE DON'T EVEN HAVE ENOUGH
FOR A SEARCH WARRANT.HE'LL KILL AGAIN. YOU--
YOU KNOW WHAT HE IS, LISBON.

09:16.120 --> 09:18.558
KNOWING ISN'T PROVING.
RIGSBY, HAVE CHO SET UP

09:18.558 --> 09:21.082
ON SYLVAN'S HOUSE
24-HOUR SURVEILLANCE.

09:21.082 --> 09:23.693
IF HE SHOWS UP, HAVE CHO FOLLOW
HIM. MAYBE WE'LL GET LUCKY.OKAY.

09:23.693 --> 09:26.870
THIS--THIS IS RIDICULOUS.
I...

09:26.870 --> 09:29.003
I KNOW.I'M GONNA GO WITH CHO. CHO!

09:29.003 --> 09:30.308
GO.

09:32.484 --> 09:35.009
SYLVAN'S SMART ENOUGH
TO KNOW WE'LL BE HERE.

09:35.009 --> 09:37.098
HE WON'T BE COMING BACK.

09:37.098 --> 09:40.014
IT'S A WASTE OF TIME.

09:40.014 --> 09:42.712
YEP.

09:44.758 --> 09:47.499
WHAT ARE YOU READING
THERE, CHO?"WUTHERING HEIGHTS."

09:49.676 --> 09:52.417
WELL,
I'M GONNA TAKE A STROLL.

09:55.856 --> 09:58.467
LET ME KNOW HOW IT ENDS.

09:58.467 --> 10:01.165
NOT WELL.

10:01.165 --> 10:06.040
[knocks on door]CHO SAID JANE DITCHED HIM
AT SYLVAN'S. HAVE YOU SEEN HIM?

10:06.040 --> 10:08.912
NOPE. THERE'S SOMETHING HINKY
HERE, BOSS.

10:08.912 --> 10:12.655
THESE ARE PHOTOS OF SOME OF
THE VICTIMS LINKED TO SYLVAN.

10:12.655 --> 10:15.266
DIFFERENT AGES,
SEXES, RACES.EXACTLY.

10:15.266 --> 10:18.792
A SERIAL KILLER ALMOST ALWAYS
HUNTS THE SAME KIND OF PREY.

10:18.792 --> 10:23.100
THIS DOESN'T MAKE SENSE
AS A SERIAL KILLER'S M.O.IT DOES WHEN YOU LOOK
AT SYLVAN'S FINANCIALS.

10:23.100 --> 10:25.929
I TRACKED BANK RECORDS FOR
ALL THE I.D.s WE COULD FIND.

10:25.929 --> 10:28.802
SYLVAN RECEIVED
SUBSTANTIAL PAYMENTS

10:28.802 --> 10:32.153
JUST BEFORE
AND JUST AFTER EACH DEATH.HE KILLS FOR MONEY?
HE'S A HIT MAN?

10:32.153 --> 10:34.242
A PSYCHOPATH WHO MADE MONEY
FROM HIS HOBBY.

10:34.242 --> 10:37.854
IT'S OUTSTANDING.
YOU DO SOMETHING YOU LOVE.

10:37.854 --> 10:41.205
YOU NEVER HAVE TO WORK
A DAY IN YOUR LIFE.WHERE THE HELL HAVE YOU BEEN?

10:41.205 --> 10:45.340
ME? OH, I'VE BEEN AROUND.I FOUND A WEB SITE REGISTERED
TO ONE OF HIS OLD IDENTITIES.

10:45.340 --> 10:47.559
IT SAYS TO "CALL MR. BLACK
FOR ODD JOBS OF ANY SORT."

10:47.559 --> 10:50.040
WELL, I GUESS
WE SHOULD GIVE HIM A CALL.

10:50.040 --> 10:51.389
UH. GRACE, DO YOU HAPPEN
TO HAVE ANY PHOTOGRAPHS

10:51.389 --> 10:54.654
OF, UH, YOU KNOW,
EX-BOYFRIENDS?

10:57.221 --> 10:59.310
I WANT YOU TO KILL HIM.

10:59.310 --> 11:01.878
HOW MUCH DO YOU CHARGE?

11:03.401 --> 11:05.142
ASK HIM AGAIN, GRACE.

11:05.142 --> 11:09.059
YOU'RE A BUSY LADY.
YOU DON'T HAVE ALL NIGHT.

11:09.059 --> 11:12.541
YOU GONNA ANSWER ME OR NOT?
I WANT THE BASTARD DEAD--SOON.OOH. SHE'S CONVINCING.

11:12.541 --> 11:15.718
SHH. TRYING TO WORK HERE.

11:15.718 --> 11:17.198
OKAY.

11:17.198 --> 11:20.201
I CHARGE $50,000.

11:20.201 --> 11:22.725
AND WHAT YOU'RE ASKING
IS PRETTY EASY.

11:22.725 --> 11:24.727
I MEAN,
YOU JUST GOTTA HAVE

11:24.727 --> 11:27.382
TO STOP THINKING OF HIM
AS A PERSON.

11:27.382 --> 11:31.908
THE REST IS JUST A PHYSICS
PROBLEM--GRAVITY, FORCE, TORQUE.

11:31.908 --> 11:33.954
ASK FOR PROOF OF WHAT HE DOES.

11:33.954 --> 11:35.999
TORQUE IS WELL AND GOOD,

11:35.999 --> 11:38.523
BUT I NEED TO KNOW
THAT YOU'RE FOR REAL.

11:38.523 --> 11:40.700
SEE, MAYBE YOU'RE A HITTER.

11:40.700 --> 11:43.006
MAYBE YOU'RE A COP.

11:43.006 --> 11:45.966
LONG SHOT.SHH! TRYING TO WORK HERE.

11:45.966 --> 11:50.144
LET ME SHOW YOU SOMETHIN'.

11:52.842 --> 11:55.366
HOW'S THAT?

11:55.366 --> 11:59.544
LET'S MOVE.NO, NO, NO. IT'S A TEST. GRACE,
LISTEN. LISTEN VERY CAREFULLY.

11:59.544 --> 12:01.764
ARE YOU A COP?

12:01.764 --> 12:03.897
I'M NOT A COP.

12:03.897 --> 12:05.594
NO?

12:05.594 --> 12:08.075
I'M JUST CAREFUL,
LIKE YOU.

12:08.075 --> 12:10.033
UH-HUH.

12:10.033 --> 12:12.079
I JUST WANT TO KNOW
THAT I HAVE THE RIGHT MAN.

12:12.079 --> 12:14.037
BESIDES, DON'T YOU WANT
TO SHOW ME...

12:14.037 --> 12:15.604
BESIDES,

12:15.604 --> 12:18.041
DON'T YOU WANT TO SHOW ME,

12:18.041 --> 12:20.696
SO YOU CAN MAKE ME AFRAID?

12:20.696 --> 12:23.960
THAT'S WHAT YOU LIKE,
ISN'T IT--

12:23.960 --> 12:26.920
SEEING THE FEAR?

12:26.920 --> 12:29.705
YOU SHOW ME YOURS,
AND I'LL SHOW YOU MINE.

12:38.366 --> 12:41.021
I HAVE SOMETHING TO SHOW YOU THEN.

12:45.416 --> 12:47.810
JUST WATCH FOR A SECOND. [Kelly shouts indistinctly]

12:47.810 --> 12:50.421
OH, WAIT. OH, PLEASE!

12:50.421 --> 12:54.121
LOOK AT IT.
IT'S MY LAST JOB. PLEASE!

12:54.121 --> 12:56.514
[muffled gunshot] AAH!

12:56.514 --> 12:59.691
THE CLIENT WAS VERY HAPPY.PROOF. THAT'S PROOF.
PROOF.

12:59.691 --> 13:01.781
ARE WE GONNA DO BUSINESS?

13:01.781 --> 13:05.045
YES, WE ARE.

13:05.045 --> 13:06.960
CBI![Lisbon] DROP THE KNIFE!

13:06.960 --> 13:08.788
DON'T MOVE!
HANDS ON YOUR HEAD![sirens wailing]

13:08.788 --> 13:11.138
[Lisbon] DROP THE KNIFE NOW!DON'T MOVE!

13:11.138 --> 13:15.925
ON YOUR KNEES!CALE SYLVAN, YOU'RE UNDER ARREST
FOR THE MURDER OF KELLY FLOWER.

13:15.925 --> 13:18.014
[police radio chatter]

13:18.014 --> 13:21.148
HANDS ON YOUR HEAD!

13:21.148 --> 13:23.933
JANE, YOU CAN COME OUT.[Patrick] OKAY.

13:23.933 --> 13:26.066
HOW'D YOU KNOW HE HAD PROOF?

13:26.066 --> 13:29.112
WELL, HE'S A NARCISSIST.
NEEDS AFFIRMATION, TROPHIES.

13:29.112 --> 13:32.594
WHO PAID YOU TO KILL KELLY?

13:32.594 --> 13:36.250
TELL 'EM.
YOU'LL FEEL BETTER.I WOULD LIKE
TO TALK TO MY LAWYER.

13:36.250 --> 13:38.600
[police radio chatter]

13:38.600 --> 13:41.690
AND I'LL SEE
YOU CLOWNS IN COURT.

13:44.171 --> 13:46.608
CATCHING KILLERS I ENJOY,

13:46.608 --> 13:48.610
BUT BEING REMINDED
THAT WE'RE JUST A COG

13:48.610 --> 13:50.960
IN A PETTY, FASCIST MACHINE--
THAT IS A LITTLE DEPRESSING.

13:50.960 --> 13:52.962
CRIME-FIGHTING IS HARD.
SUCK IT UP.

13:52.962 --> 13:54.921
IF YOU WEREN'T
ON THE WITNESS LIST,

13:54.921 --> 13:56.966
I WOULDN'T EVEN LET YOU

13:56.966 --> 13:59.055
IN THE SAME TIME ZONE
AS JUDGE DREAD.

13:59.055 --> 14:02.145
"JUDGE DREAD"--CAN'T POSSIBLY
BE AS MUCH FUN AS IT SOUNDS.

14:02.145 --> 14:06.976
[Sylvan speaks indistinctly] OH, PLEASE! PLEASE!

