NOWHERE NEAR THE DOCKS.

31:50.169 --> 31:52.345
WELL, THAT'S GOOD.
IT'S A TERRIBLE NEIGHBORHOOD.

31:52.345 --> 31:54.347
YOU SAID YOU CALLED ME
BECAUSE I WAS CLOSER,

31:54.347 --> 31:56.958
