32:41.872 --> 32:43.309
HELLO!HELLO?

32:43.309 --> 32:44.919
OVER HERE!IN HERE!

32:44.919 --> 32:47.052
AROUND THE FRONT.
THE--THE BIG LATCH.

32:47.052 --> 32:50.446
I TOLD YOU
I WOULD SAVE YOU, LISBON.[chuckles]

32:50.446 --> 32:53.101
[Patrick] WHAT?

32:55.321 --> 32:59.194
[bleats]

32:59.194 --> 33:00.282
HEY.

33:14.079 --> 33:16.907
SAC P.D. FOUND JANE'S CAR
AT THE DOCKS. LISBON'S, TOO.[whispers] CRAP.

33:16.907 --> 33:19.867
NO SIGN OF THEM
OR THE DRABERS.CALL SAC P.D., I.C.E.
AND THE COAST GUARD.

33:19.867 --> 33:22.304
HAVE THEM SEARCH
EVERY VEHICLE...[telephone rings]

33:22.304 --> 33:25.351
WAREHOUSE AND BOAT
THE DRABERS OWN.VAN PELT. O-OH. SLOW DOWN.

33:25.351 --> 33:27.875
AGENT RIGSBY.UM, Sí. UNO--UNO MOMENTO,
POR FAVOR.

33:27.875 --> 33:30.486
CAN YOU?I'LL CALL YOU BACK.

33:30.486 --> 33:32.967
[hangs up receiver]IT'S THE FEDERALES, I THINK.

33:32.967 --> 33:35.926
UH...SOMETHING ABOUT JANE
AND A GOAT?

33:38.581 --> 33:40.931
LOUISE WILLETT ROBBED

33:40.931 --> 33:43.934
THE VERY PEOPLE SHE WAS
SUPPOSED TO BE TAKING CARE OF,

33:43.934 --> 33:45.893
AND SHE SPENT THAT MONEY--IPSO FACTO, AD NAUSEAM.

33:45.893 --> 33:48.896
SORRY, ODENTHAL. I NEED TO
BORROW YOUR JUDGE FOR A SECOND.

33:48.896 --> 33:52.552
[clears throat] UH, MR. JANE,
WE ARE IN SESSION.YES, WE WOULD HAVE
COME EARLIER,

33:52.552 --> 33:55.337
BUT, UH, WE HAD
QUITE A LONG WALK GETTING HERE.

33:55.337 --> 33:57.948
IT WON'T TAKE A SECOND.
WE JUST NEED

33:57.948 --> 34:01.169
ONE OF YOUR FANCY ARREST/WARRANT
THINGIES FOR ANNABELLE DRABER.[cell phone rings]

