$3,000.LISTEN, CHO, UH...

34:18.447 --> 34:21.842
$4,000.YOUR HONOR,
I MOVE FOR A MISTRIAL.

34:21.842 --> 34:24.975
$5,000.YOU'RE NOT COSTING ME ANOTHER
CASE. GIVE ME THAT PHONE.

34:24.975 --> 34:28.152
NO. GET YOUR OWN.YOUR HONOR--BATTERY?

