37:09.444 --> 37:11.490
THE PERSON
THAT KILLED CALE SYLVAN,

37:11.490 --> 37:13.318
THEY ESTIMATED,
WAS MORE THAN 200 YARDS AWAY.

37:13.318 --> 37:15.581
