37:56.361 --> 37:59.233
OH, THAT'S NOT BAD.
NOT--NOT BAD AT ALL.

37:59.233 --> 38:01.888
10-GAUGE, 3-INCH SHELL.
3 INCHES OF HELL.

38:01.888 --> 38:03.542
3 INCHES OF DEATH.

38:03.542 --> 38:04.934
3 1/2.

38:07.415 --> 38:10.070
