AROUND A GUN, DON'T YOU?

38:27.479 --> 38:31.483
OH, RELAX. IT'S NOT LOADED.

38:31.483 --> 38:34.268
YOU OWN YOUR OWN RIFLE,
DON'T YOU?

38:36.139 --> 38:38.359
YOU HEARD THAT THE JUDGE
