38:58.858 --> 39:02.731
YOUR HONOR,
THIS IS COMPLETELY RIDICULOUS.SO PROVE IT.
LET US SEARCH YOUR HOUSE.

39:02.731 --> 39:06.605
WE DON'T FIND A GUN,
