39:06.605 --> 39:08.694
LET HIM DO THE SEARCH, MARC.

39:08.694 --> 39:10.522
NO.

39:10.522 --> 39:11.697
NO?

39:11.697 --> 39:15.091
NO.
I DON'T HAVE TO DO THAT.

